163
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:40,950
It must be that she seriously fell in love with me.

164
00:09:40,950 --> 00:09:44,000
Sunohara. Why don't you think about Mei-chan a-

165
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:47,740
