215
00:12:00,650 --> 00:12:03,070
But love is a person's choice.

216
00:12:14,940 --> 00:12:16,010
Onii-chan?

217
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:19,460
Sorry. It's me.

218
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:44,450
I understand how you got upset at him,
but wasn't that a little much?

219
00:12:44,450 --> 00:12:47,950
